{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/projects/ascensionv0.0.1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7ca5b844-fcd2-59a1-9ca8-6f68cc5a7c7d","html":"<figure style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 58.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/8ac56/ascension.webp 240w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/d3be9/ascension.webp 480w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/e46b2/ascension.webp 960w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/f992d/ascension.webp 1440w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/882b9/ascension.webp 1920w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/00ea7/ascension.webp 6744w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/8ff5a/ascension.png 240w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/e85cb/ascension.png 480w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/d9199/ascension.png 960w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/07a9c/ascension.png 1440w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/29114/ascension.png 1920w,\n/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/7bebe/ascension.png 6744w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/d9199/ascension.png\" alt=\"wip title page\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Roguelike Game adapted from the novel TGCF</figcaption><br>\n  <b><div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/kayleecragg/ascension/releases/download/v0.0.1/Ascension_32.zip\" target=\"_blank\">Play (Windows)</a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/kayleecragg/ascension/releases/download/beta/Ascension_osx.zip\" target=\"_blank\">Play (Mac, older version)</a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/kayleecragg/ascension\" target=\"_blank\">Github</a>\n  </div>\n  <b>\n</b></b></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>Built a 2D narrative action game in <strong>Lua’s Löve2D</strong> framework, featuring real-time combat with melee, ranged, teleport, and dodge mechanics, plus wave-based scaling enemies and branching dialogue sequences.</li>\n<li>Made this game with a <a href=\"https://github.com/its-naptime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">friend</a>, you can watch a video of our progress <a href=\"https://youtu.be/FHOgZQkW0RY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Spoilers for the novel and game upcoming.</p>\n<h2 id=\"background\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#background\" aria-label=\"background permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Background</h2>\n<p>Having recently finished reading all 8 volumes of the very popular Chinese danmei novel series <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heaven_Official%27s_Blessing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Heaven Official’s Blessings</strong></a>, <em>(aka 天官赐福 Tiān Guān Cì Fú)</em> I was moved by how Hua Cheng gave up his life twice in service to his God, spent 800 years searching for him, and remained his sole believer when all others had abandoned him.</p>\n<p>I wished they explored more of his backstory and his point of view. Here are some excerpts from the novel to show you how interesting of a character he was:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>At one point in his time as a Supreme, Hua Cheng challenged 35 gods. 33 of them were those that chased away Xie Lian from the spiritual mountain, as well as Mu Qing and Feng Xin. If they won against him, he would give them his ashes to scatter. If he won, they would have to step down from Heaven. Mu Qing and Feng Xin both ignored the challenge, but the others took it on as they believed themselves to be superior. He fought the Martial Gods and debated against the Civil Gods, resulting in their utter defeat.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>However, the gods refused to honor their agreement, pretending that the fight and the preceding agreement never took place. Hua Cheng decided to help them fulfill their promise by burning down the 33 gods’ temples in the human realm. This act caused an uproar and Hua Cheng got the moniker “Heaven’s Scourge”.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I wanted to make a game from his perspective. I also was inspired by twitter user <a href=\"https://x.com/akkaccel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">@akkaccel’s</a> concept art of a potential TGCF game.</p>\n<figure>\n  <a href=\"https://x.com/akkaccel/status/1493084468537659393?s=46\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 45.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/8ac56/tgcfrpg.webp 240w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/d3be9/tgcfrpg.webp 480w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/e46b2/tgcfrpg.webp 960w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/f992d/tgcfrpg.webp 1440w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/882b9/tgcfrpg.webp 1920w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/554c2/tgcfrpg.webp 2188w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/09b79/tgcfrpg.jpg 240w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/7cc5e/tgcfrpg.jpg 480w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/6a068/tgcfrpg.jpg 960w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/644c5/tgcfrpg.jpg 1440w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/0f98f/tgcfrpg.jpg 1920w,\n/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/e3029/tgcfrpg.jpg 2188w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/a96ea30fd1eaa5ad3adaea3888ee466c/6a068/tgcfrpg.jpg\" alt=\"tgcfrpg\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  </a>\n  <figcaption>one of four of twitter user @akkaccel's concept art for a potential TGCF video game</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>There were a few main areas I could start from:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Being saved by Xie Lian as a child.</li>\n<li>Him sneaking off to be a soldier to fight against Yong’an.</li>\n<li>Ghost fire adventures (my favourite personally)</li>\n<li>Wuming</li>\n<li>Mt Tonglu adventures</li>\n<li>Challenging 35 Heavenly Officials</li>\n<li>Meeting Xie Lian again + main story</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I decided to go with the 33 heavenly officials plot because it seemed the most clear cut narrative and straightforward gameplay; fighting people, maybe Ace Attorney style debating, maybe some burning down of temples.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/8ac56/outline.webp 240w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/d3be9/outline.webp 480w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/e46b2/outline.webp 960w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/f992d/outline.webp 1440w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/882b9/outline.webp 1920w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/cf8e6/outline.webp 7680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/8ff5a/outline.png 240w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/e85cb/outline.png 480w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/d9199/outline.png 960w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/07a9c/outline.png 1440w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/29114/outline.png 1920w,\n/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/c841b/outline.png 7680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/440a7f7e6b1d138c6ab703ca7208124f/d9199/outline.png\" alt=\"outline\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Gameplay Sequence Flow Diagram</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"the-first-prototype\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-first-prototype\" aria-label=\"the first prototype permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The First Prototype</h2>\n<h3 id=\"first-day\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#first-day\" aria-label=\"first day permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>First Day</h3>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/d6a75b837589fe351a76286f9c1002bc/prototype.gif\" alt=\"prototype of the game\">\n  <figcaption>Early prototype footage, made a simple single file, single enemy game to show to friends</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>I started off by making a single file, single enemy game to get a feel for what it would be like. I chose to make the game in <strong>Lua</strong> because firstly, I was hooked on playing Balatro at that time and learnt that Balatro was made in Lua, specifically <strong>Löve2D</strong>, a lightweight framework that had endless potential and possibilities, and was known to be good for making 2D games in.</p>\n<p>And secondly, I didn’t think I could start out with anything but a 2D rendition of the game I had in mind. I didn’t know anything about Unreal Engine, and I didn’t think I had the time to master it to make a game with it that quickly. Also the last time I tried to install Unreal Engine 5 on my mac it sounded like a jet taking off.</p>\n<p>So currently what we had was:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Player ranged attacks</li>\n<li>Player teleport ability with NO cooldown</li>\n<li>Enemy follows player around but doesn’t attack</li>\n<li>300hp for both player and enemy</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"second-day\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#second-day\" aria-label=\"second day permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Second Day</h3>\n<p>The next day, I added some dialogue options and a placeholder debate section.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/8ac56/ascension1.webp 240w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/d3be9/ascension1.webp 480w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/e46b2/ascension1.webp 960w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/f992d/ascension1.webp 1440w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/882b9/ascension1.webp 1920w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/e51ec/ascension1.webp 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/8ff5a/ascension1.png 240w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/e85cb/ascension1.png 480w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/d9199/ascension1.png 960w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/07a9c/ascension1.png 1440w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/29114/ascension1.png 1920w,\n/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/669cd/ascension1.png 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/e05e5c7f6d9124d904ccb21530935816/d9199/ascension1.png\" alt=\"hua cheng\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Gameplay still of Hua Cheng</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/8ac56/ascension2.webp 240w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/d3be9/ascension2.webp 480w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/e46b2/ascension2.webp 960w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/f992d/ascension2.webp 1440w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/882b9/ascension2.webp 1920w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/e51ec/ascension2.webp 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/8ff5a/ascension2.png 240w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/e85cb/ascension2.png 480w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/d9199/ascension2.png 960w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/07a9c/ascension2.png 1440w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/29114/ascension2.png 1920w,\n/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/669cd/ascension2.png 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/0af8f6236920b26e2e1cd84b5e3bdd3e/d9199/ascension2.png\" alt=\"angry heavenly official\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Gameplay image of masked out image of Shi Qing Xuan, though the dialogue doesn't fit his personality</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>I showed this version to my friends, and one of my friends said he wanted to contribute, so that very night we started working on it together. I thought I should implement a wave structure to the game to make it more longlasting.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAANCAIAAAAmMtkJAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAeElEQVR42mOIi42Oj43BRHEx0eGhIUASqyxEAQNFgIWZGRdixi0FQQyDDDAxMVKkn5GRkYmJCcQgSRsHJ7NfsDQ7OwupGkGAjY3JzFyIlY0FwhVgY2ZnZiLNzcB4gtgbIMGnzM1GgvuBGiEexmcBpbHCTC5gZWEGAIkiGbX8GNIuAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/8ac56/ascension3.webp 240w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/d3be9/ascension3.webp 480w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/e46b2/ascension3.webp 960w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/f992d/ascension3.webp 1440w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/882b9/ascension3.webp 1920w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/e51ec/ascension3.webp 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/8ff5a/ascension3.png 240w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/e85cb/ascension3.png 480w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/d9199/ascension3.png 960w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/07a9c/ascension3.png 1440w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/29114/ascension3.png 1920w,\n/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/669cd/ascension3.png 3024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/92ad17a42fae8413598ae23e1156590d/d9199/ascension3.png\" alt=\"gameplay preview\" title=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Early ranged attack gameplay preview</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<ul>\n<li>6 Waves</li>\n<li>Player 300 hp >> 100 hp</li>\n<li>Player and enemy health bars instead of a number</li>\n<li>enemies attack u</li>\n<li>diff kinds of enemies (ranged, charging, melee)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bugs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>teleport feature too broken (TOO GOOD), there was no range and the cooldown was ridiculously low</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/d523467c9bbd8e6878805dbbd9a1eee0/gif_teleport.gif\">\n  <figcaption>playtesting the teleport feature</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<ul>\n<li>glitch: cannot die</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/9c6b2a8f02341ab46529b17ca30b75af/gif_glitchimmortal.gif\">\n  <figcaption>while playtesting we ran into a glitch where the player does not take damage from certain actions</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h3 id=\"third-day\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#third-day\" aria-label=\"third day permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Third Day</h3>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/d0a13dfea2b903ff81e0b65e5ea89f2a/gif_difficulty.gif\">\n  <figcaption>My friend commenting on the difficulty level of the game</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<ul>\n<li>dodge ability</li>\n<li>teleport limited range</li>\n<li>balancing for enemies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bugs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>dodge slowing down time literally, it pauses the game</li>\n<li>you can’t move when teleporting</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/4fb779c92c26e88acbc6e9ab38309446/gif_badteleport1.gif\">\n  <figcaption>While playtesting, we found a bug where you can't move while casting teleport.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/fc477a874a7100efe6bd7969eb9fd062/gif_badteleport.gif\">\n  <figcaption>We realised it was unintuitive and unsatisfying to use</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h3 id=\"fourth-day\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fourth-day\" aria-label=\"fourth day permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fourth Day</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>can move during teleport</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/4a83ff6c1338b4d8101020dd91f43e4f/gif_goodteleport.gif\">\n  <figcaption>teleport bug fixed so you can now move when activating teleport</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<ul>\n<li>dodge no longer slows time</li>\n<li>health regen orbs drop when enemies die</li>\n</ul>\n<figure>\n  <img src=\"/ad49abbf39435ce2ad46400c37860114/gif_orbdrop.gif\">\n  <figcaption>health regen orb drops</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>Bugs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>health regen drop too low chance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>WIP, more to come.</em></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2025-05-07---ascension//projects/ascensionv0.0.1","tagSlugs":["/tag/development/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2025-05-07T11:46:37.121Z","tags":["development"],"title":"Ascension v0.0.1","description":"Roguelike 2D Game made in Lua and with Love2D adapted from the novel TGCF.","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/e2ae7689a69c9796a327ab1fd6d40308/ascension.png"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2025-05-07---ascension//projects/ascensionv0.0.1"}},"staticQueryHashes":["4208939363"],"slicesMap":{}}